General.Name: Ausquest Ltd
General.Description: AusQuest Limited explores and evaluates mineral resources in Australia and Peru. The company explores for copper, iron oxide, gold, zinc, and nickel deposits. It holds approximately 7,300km² of exploration title within Australia, which includes 6,800km² within Western Australia and 500km² within Queensland. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is based in Ardross, Australia.
